wrapContent.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE cXML SYSTEM "http://xml.cXML.org/schemas/cXML/1.2.044/cXML.dtd"> 
<cXML timestamp="${header.CurrentTS}" payloadID="${header.IBPQueryUUID}" xml:lang = "en">
    <Header>
        <From>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkId">
                <Identity>${header.AribaSupplierANID}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </From>
        <To>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkID">
                <Identity>AN01000000001</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </To>
        <Sender>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkId">
                <Identity>${header.AribaSupplierANID}</Identity>
                <SharedSecret>${header.AribaSharedSecret}</SharedSecret>
            </Credential>
            <UserAgent>Ariba IBP User</UserAgent>
        </Sender>
    </Header> 
    <Request deploymentMode="test">
        <DataRequest>
            <InternalID domain="PendingMessages">${property.MessageId}</InternalID>
        </DataRequest>
    </Request>
</cXML>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE cXML SYSTEM "http://xml.cXML.org/schemas/cXML/1.2.044/cXML.dtd">
<cXML timestamp="${header.CurrentTS}" payloadID="${header.IBPQueryUUID}" xml:lang = "en">
    <Header>
        <From>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkId">
                <Identity>${header.AribaSupplierANID}</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </From>
        <To>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkID">
                <Identity>AN01000000001</Identity>
            </Credential>
        </To>
        <Sender>
            <Credential domain = "NetworkId">
                 <Identity>${header.AribaSupplierANID}</Identity>
                <SharedSecret>${header.AribaSharedSecret}</SharedSecret>
            </Credential>
            <UserAgent>Ariba IBP User</UserAgent>
        </Sender>
    </Header>
 <Request deploymentMode="test">
        <GetPendingRequest lastReceivedTimestamp="${property.lastReceivedPATimeStamp}" maxMessages="${header.MaxToDownload}">
            <MessageType>${header.AribaMessageType}</MessageType>
        </GetPendingRequest>
    </Request>
</cXML>
